 Sparklight estate  “There might be a reduction in FDIs returns. There is hope and foreign investors would still come in because opportunities lay within Africa and we haven’t started to scratch the surface. If you take co-working, for example, is a new concept in Africa and come outside COVID 19, you are going to see a huge number of investment in co-working spaces. People are going to change in line with the dynamic of the market.”
   
